{"tid":184282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【估唔到呀】舉起雪糕相機食先 點知發生「悲劇」","createTime":"2017-04-02T16:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T13:13:31.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"903cc3ea3d7ef2519f736b209893f451adea2377","tid":184282,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:32:17.000Z","msg":"2017年04月03日<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170402/large/1491110362_847f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170402%2Flarge%2F1491110362_847f.jpg&h=4875d703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「相機食先」是互聯網世代的指定動作，但美食是不等人的。美國加州一位女大學生就受到了慘痛的教訓。<br />\n<br />\n20歲網民「@youngweonhi」就讀於加州大學，上周她趁春假到加州聖巴巴拉(Santa Barbara）海邊欣賞美景，在和暖的天氣下，買來一支雪糕享受一番，她伸長手臂舉起雪糕，讓美食和美景相結合，準備拍下完美的照片。<br />\n「悲劇」卻就此發生了。正當她拍攝時，一隻可惡的海鷗乘虛而入，抓住雪糕筒邊沿毫不客氣便啄下雪糕，大快朵頭，然後更悲慘的是，整個雪糕跌入大海中。她上載海鷗「犯案」的照片並寫道：「我不敢相信這竟然發生了，安息吧我的雪糕。」網民看罷照片，寄予同情之餘又忍不住大笑。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170403/56512364\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170403%2F56512364&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=dd9487c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170403%2F56512364&h=87e37aa1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170403/56512364</a>"},{"pid":"e11251bc6f600d24ada2954e1cffca6956a2e784","tid":184282,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:33:48.000Z","msg":"海鷗: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad815108e12853751269675cd62a22eb14a33c4","tid":184282,"uid":65384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:39:24.000Z","msg":"我都試過俾海鷗搶左個漢堡包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死海鷗我dllm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007bfb8844a4f54616fc68a1a14d8ef91404b187","tid":184282,"uid":16085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:40:33.000Z","msg":"有冇敏感牙齒呢<br />\n<br />\n然後可以拍廣告"},{"pid":"b5dce663e89771781db0458b3de716df894085d1","tid":184282,"uid":85556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9308b65f3780d2ad61b050052fa8bd1401a00c99","tid":184282,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:42:35.000Z","msg":"識食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11178352605f94fae2988654fa054fff0920b213","tid":184282,"uid":94452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f658424017e71e3405d52206acfbfb9d21fa03","tid":184282,"uid":8569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:51:16.000Z","msg":"仲好啦 張相仲多d人睇到同like 佢都係想咁姐"},{"pid":"bd3238f0fa58c55d143c3d9f2368aa2abc216a98","tid":184282,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:24:59.000Z","msg":"邊關事，<br />\n<br />\nd人餵開雀，就係拎住野食舉起手，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家隻雀見你又舉起手，咪以為你餵佢，佢咪飛落黎食lor<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人地點知你其實影緊相咩"},{"pid":"33fc1dacf32683b671e8052b9ab0759fce8c8753","tid":184282,"uid":82317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:57:28.000Z","msg":"其實條女特登引雀黎食<br />\n唔係點呃like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713aa89363bf2016d24c7b8a5486bfb0a36e3087","tid":184282,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:01:29.000Z","msg":"對個女仔呢講，影到呢張相仲好過食雪糕"},{"pid":"d73721f9642f6dd28fe325de02b6bbd7f469bd58","tid":184282,"uid":